race.comment: FRENCH EMPIRE (3) was rewarded with his maiden success last start, scoring by 1.75 lengths over 1200m at Jundah. Shaping up nicely and he can go right on with it now. BITTERBLUE (8) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1200m at Richmond Qld, beaten 5 lengths into fifth. Meets some better types this time but this looks well within his grasp. COMBS (2) didn't make an impact at his last run before going for a spell on 7/08/2025, finishing fifth and beaten 5.5 lengths over 1450m at this track. Has to be respected. CORVALIST (1) registered his first win last start over 1000m at Cloncurry, getting home by 0.8 lengths. Michael McDonald was in the saddle on that occasion and retains the mount. Must be respected now that the penny has dropped.
